name: Premantura
---
pois:

44.795733 | 13.923626 | Premantura, Croatia | General sailing area.
---
body: A very popular spot for catching the Bora wind. Most of the people use the camping side. They have daily passes if you just go sailing there. Can get crowded. Booties are recommended due to sharp rocks with plenty of sea urchins.

Also popular as a freeride venue in Southerlies.
